trans-unit.source: Enables developers to override the rendering for only the selected sections of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Gjør det mulig for utviklere å overstyre gjengivelse for de valgte delene av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.source: Chrome refers to the peripheral user interface (UI) elements that frame each Web Parts control or server control contained in a zone.
trans-unit.target: Chrome refererer til de eksterne elementene i brukergrensesnittet (UI) rammen hver webdeler kontroll eller serverkontroll finnes i en sone.

trans-unit.source: The chrome for a control includes its border, its title bar, and the icons, title text, and verbs menu that appear within the title bar.
trans-unit.target: Chrome for en kontroll inneholder kantlinjen, tittellinjen, og ikonene, titteltekst og verb menyen som vises i tittellinjen.

trans-unit.source: The appearance of the chrome is set at the zone level, and applies to all the controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Utseendet til chrome er angitt på zone-nivå, og gjelder for alle kontroller i sonen.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control set uses the EditorPartChrome class to render the chrome for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Settet med webdeler kontrollen inneholder klassen EditorPartChrome for å gjengi chrome for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, this class provides a way for developers to customize the rendering of any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg denne klassen inneholder en metode for utviklere å tilpasse gjengivelse av noen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.CreateEditorPartChromeStyle%2A> method to customize some specific style attributes defined in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.CreateEditorPartChromeStyle%2A>metode for å tilpasse noen bestemt stil attributtene som er definert i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.CreateEditorPartChromeStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The EditorPartChrome class contains several important methods that are useful when you want to override the rendering of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen EditorPartChrome inneholder flere viktige metoder som er nyttig når du vil overstyre gjengivelse av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: One is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.%23ctor%2A> constructor, which you use when you override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.CreateEditorPartChrome%2A> method in a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> class to create an instance of your custom EditorPartChrome object.
trans-unit.target: En er den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør som du bruker når du overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.CreateEditorPartChrome%2A>metoden i en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>klassen for å opprette en forekomst av det egendefinerte EditorPartChrome-objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.CreateEditorPartChrome%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Another useful method is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A> method, which you can use to control the rendering of the content area of controls in a zone (as opposed to chrome elements such as headers, footers, and title bars).
trans-unit.target: En annen nyttig metode er den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A>metode, som du kan bruke til å kontrollere gjengivelse av området innhold i kontroller i en sone (i motsetning til chrome elementer som topptekst, bunntekst og tittellinjer).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, if you want complete programmatic control over all aspects of rendering the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls, you can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.RenderEditorPart%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt Hvis du vil fullføre programmatisk kontroll over alle aspekter ved gjengivelse av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller, du kan overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.RenderEditorPart%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome.RenderEditorPart%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The EditorPartChrome constructor initializes a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren EditorPartChrome initialiserer en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome>

trans-unit.source: It is used primarily by an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone in its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.CreateEditorPartChrome%2A> method to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome> object that handles the chrome rendering and any custom rendering for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Det brukes hovedsakelig av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>sone i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.CreateEditorPartChrome%2A>metode for å opprette en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome>objekt som behandler chrome gjengivelsen og egendefinert gjengivelse for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller i sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.CreateEditorPartChrome%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>

trans-unit.target: Oppretter stil-objektet som leverer oppstår for hver <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen gjengis av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartChrome"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The PerformPreRender method allows you to perform tasks that must be done during the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender> event and cannot be done when the control is rendered, such as applying a style sheet to a control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden PerformPreRender kan du utføre oppgaver som må utføres under den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender>hendelse og kan ikke utføres når kontrollen gjengis, for eksempel å bruke en stilarket til en kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender>

trans-unit.source: Renders a complete <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control with all its sections.
trans-unit.target: Gjengivelser et fullstendig <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroll med alle delene.

trans-unit.source: The RenderEditorPart method renders the complete <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> control, with header, contents, and footer.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RenderEditorPart gjengir det fullstendige <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroll med topptekst, innholdet og bunntekst.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Overriding this method gives a developer complete programmatic control over rendering all aspects of `editorPart`; for that reason, overriding this method is quite complex.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer denne metoden gir utvikler full programmatisk kontroll over gjengivelse alle aspekter ved `editorPart`; derfor overstyrer denne metoden er helt kompleks.

trans-unit.source: The RenderPartContents method enables you to override the rendering of the body area of `editorPart`, while leaving rendering of the header and footer to the default rendering.
